Name: pitchly
Version: 0.0.0
Summary: A python package that is a wrapper for Plotly to generate football tracking and event data plots
Home-page: https://github.com/opunsoars/pitchly
Author: Vinay Warrier
Author-email: vinay.warrier@gmail.com
